desc: Canada Nutra's goal is to design high-quality pet supplements for our customers' companions. Our partnering facilities are GMP, FDA, and Health Canada Compliant. We are proudly Canadian and all our products are 100% made in Canada. Our first supplement brand, Canine Nutra, is designed for dogs of all ages and size.

layout.text: When I found out about Canine Nutra, I liked it a lot because it is sourced from natural ingredients with no synthetic chemicals that alter the nervous system but quite the opposite. It's also authorized by Health Canada, so I decided to put it to the test. During walks her behavior changed completely, she stopped stretching the leash, and the walks are now more enjoyable as her attitude has stayed the same. She's just simply calmer without losing her energy and mood.
